---
title: One-Pot Kidney Bean & Pepper Soup with Blue Corn Tortilla Chips, Monterey Jack & Sour Cream
description: Soup-er supper alert! Just one spoonful of this hearty, richly spiced soup will warm you from the inside out. Kidney beans simmer with Southwest spices, sautéed onion, and green pepper until thickened. The soup’s then served loaded up with all the fixin’s: sour cream, Monterey Jack cheese, and cilantro, plus blue corn tortilla chips on the side for dipping. Oh, happy belly!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/665dee2507c68e1e8bb69aec-f1538cc1.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/665dee2507c68e1e8bb69aec-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pot-kidney-bean-and-pepper-soup-665dee2507c68e1e8bb69aec
cuisine: Mexican
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 620 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 76 g
  sugar: 22 g
  protein: 20 g
  fiber: 14 g
  sodium: 1790 mg
---

Wash and dry produce.

Halve, peel, and dice @onion{1}(halved, peeled, and diced). Core, deseed, and
finely dice @long green pepper{1}(cored, deseeded, and finely diced).

Heat a drizzle of @cooking oil{1%tsp} in a #medium pot{} (use a large pot for
4 servings) over medium-high heat. Add onion and green pepper; cook, stirring
occasionally, until browned and softened, ~{5-7%minutes}.

Stir in @crushed tomatoes{1%13.76oz can} and
@Southwest spice blend{1%tbsp} until combined; cook until fragrant,
~{1%minute}.

Stir @kidney beans{1%410g can} and their liquid, @Tex-Mex paste{1%unit},
@veggie stock concentrate{1%unit}, and 1/2 cup water (1 cup for 4 servings)
into pot with veggies.

Bring to a simmer, then reduce heat to medium low. Cook, stirring often, until
flavors meld and soup has slightly thickened, ~{8-10%minutes}. Taste and
season with @salt{} and @pepper{}. TIP: Add a splash more water if the soup
ends up thicker than you like.

Meanwhile, pick @cilantro{1/4%oz} leaves from stems.

Divide soup between #bowls{} and dollop with @sour cream{3%tbsp}. Sprinkle with
@Monterey Jack cheese{1/4%cup} and cilantro leaves. Serve with
@blue corn tortilla chips{1.5%oz} on the side for dipping.